## ðŸ“Œ Project Overview
This Power BI dashboard analyzes HR data to identify patterns and key factors contributing to employee attrition.  
It covers insights such as attrition rate by department, job role, salary, age group, education field, and more.

---

## ðŸŽ¯ Key Insights
- Attrition % by Department & Gender
- Average Monthly Income by Job Role
- Attrition trend based on Age Groups
- Impact of Business Travel on Attrition
- Education Field vs Attrition
- Job & Environment Satisfaction Levels

